C++17 program that demonstrates almost all console I/O techniques.

How to use this program
    Run it step-by-step and observe:
        Try different inputs
        Comment/uncomment sections
        Mix cin and scanf to see behavior
        Modify buffer reads

Key learning from this
    This single file shows:
        High-level → cin / cout
        Mid-level → get / put / read / write
        Parsing → stringstream
        Formatting → iomanip
        Low-level → getchar / putchar
        Performance → fast I/O flags
        UI tricks → \r, flush